# For Cloudflare Workers local dev (`wrangler dev`), put non-secret env values here
# in a `.dev.vars` file (Wrangler reads that automatically). Secrets like MCP_ACCESS_KEY
# should be set via `wrangler secret put MCP_ACCESS_KEY` so they never land in git.
#
# iCount creds are NOT here — they come from per-request headers
# (Authorization: Bearer ..., X-Icount-Cid: ...).

# Optional: shared secret. If set, every request must include header `X-Mcp-Key: <this value>`.
# MCP_ACCESS_KEY=
